                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>to you at present worthy almost of mention.<lb/> Today is the <date>third day of\n                    Pesach</date>, and<lb/> so far the synagogues were well attended,<lb/> and many\n                families, most of them keep it<lb/> &amp; have Mazoes; to give you a proof of<lb/>\n                the general observance, I might only tell<lb/> you that one man has sold $160\n                worth<lb/> of horse radish necessary to the Ceder<lb/> ceremony.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">The Committee appointed to give out<lb/> proposals &amp;c have not\n                as yet determined<lb/> their labors; but it is decided that the<lb/> cost of the\n                building alone would not exceed<lb/> the amt. of $20.00—; for this money a<lb/> fair\n                building<lb/> can be put up.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I would like you to speak in some laudable<lb/> terms of the “<hi\n                    rend=\"underline\">Young Men's Debating<lb/> Society</hi>” in the next number of\n                the Occi-<lb/>-dent. This Society is only about 6 weeks<lb/> in existence &amp; has\n                already between 30 &amp;<lb/> 40 members; the object of the Society is<lb/> for the\n                improvement in debating in discussing various<lb/> kinds of questions. The Society\n                is composed<lb/> of young men of our persuasion, but the<lb/> zeal, energy &amp;\n                rivalry, and the interest taken<lb/> &amp; manifested by the young men does\n                really<lb/> honor and reflect great credit upon the Jewish<lb/> young men in\n                    <placeName>San Francisco</placeName>. <persName>Mr.<lb/> S. C. Labatt</persName>\n                is President.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Please give my kind regards to <persName>Mr. M. Allen</persName></p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p31n7z707/canvas/p2"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
