                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>and please mention to him that I<lb/> have recd his letter &amp; shall answer it<lb/>\n                soon.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\"><persName>Mr. and Mrs. Roggenburger</persName> request me<lb/> to\n                give their kind regards to you,<lb/> &amp; trusting this may find<lb/> you in the\n                enjoyment of<lb/> good health</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(5)\">I remain</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(6)\">Yours truly</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(7)\">(Signed) <persName role=\"author\">Cauffman H. Meyer</persName></p>\n            <p>Excuse my bad writing as I</p>\n            <p>have written this in great haste.</p>\n            <div>\n                <p>\n                    <ref target=\"Occident_PDFs/Occ_12_4.pdf\">The above text refers to Occident\n                        Volume 12 No. 4 pages 229 through 230. Click here to view.</ref>\n                </p>\n            </div>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p31n7z707/canvas/p3"
